QuestData.Title: Work Order: Shado-Pan II
QuestData.Description: Well, your work is done for the day! Now to wait for the harvest tomorrow.$b$bOnce your green cabbages are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.$b$bOnly the finest cabbage will do for the Shado-Pan!
QuestData.LogDescription: Harvest 8 Ripe Green Cabbage plants and provide 40 Green Cabbages for the Shado-Pan.
